snippet.title: Celebrity WotNot
snippet.description:
Your Source for Positive & Fun Celebrity News. Organic Celebrity News You Might Say 😁  We also give away free Celebrity Images...

Subscribe to our channel if you love celebs as much as we do. We never upload videos of celebrity children because it's dangerous and we never post embarrassing or salacious videos. Celebrities have feelings too! 

We upload a new video daily. Don't miss out!

Visit our Celebrity WotNot website for more great coverage: https://www.celebritywotnot.com
